Signed-off-by: Alex Deucher <alexander.deucher@amd.com>
(cherry picked from commit a7c0cad0dc060bb77e9c9d235d68441b0fc69507)
Signed-off-by: Cristian Ciocaltea <cristian.ciocaltea@collabora.com>
